r shall each one teach his neighbor and each his brother, saying, \u2018Know the <span class=\"nd\">Lord</span>,\u2019 for they shall all know me, from the least of them to the greatest, declares the <span class=\"nd\">Lord</span>. For I will forgive their iniquity, and I will remember their sin no more.\u201d</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v24_31_35\"><sup id=\"Jer.31.35\" class=\"v24_31_35\">35</sup>Thus says the <span class=\"nd\">Lord</span>,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v24_31_35\">who gives the sun for light by day</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v24_31_35\">and the fixed order of the moon and the stars for light by night,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v24_31_35\">who stirs up the sea so that its waves roar\u2014</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v24_31_35\">the <span class=\"nd\">Lord</span> of hosts is his name:</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v24_31_36\"><sup id=\"Jer.31.36\" class=\"v24_31_36\">36</sup>\u201cIf this fixed order departs</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v24_31_36\">from before me, declares the <span class=\"nd\">Lord</span>,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v24_31_36\">then shall the offspring of Israel cease</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v24_31_36\">from being a nation before me forever.\u201d</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v24_31_37\"><sup id=\"Jer.31.37\" class=\"v24_31_37\">37</sup>Thus says the <span class=\"nd\">Lord</span>:</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v24_31_37\">\u201cIf the heavens above can be measured,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v24_31_37\">and the foundations of the earth below can be explored,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v24_31_37\">then I will cast off all the offspring of Israel</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v24_31_37\">for all that they have done,</span></p>\n<p class=\"qr\"><span class=\"v24_31_37\">declares the <span class=\"