isten to me. </span><span class=\"v24_35_16\"><sup id=\"Jer.35.16\" class=\"v24_35_16\">16</sup>The sons of Jonadab the son of Rechab have kept the command that their father gave them, but this people has not obeyed me. </span><span class=\"v24_35_17\"><sup id=\"Jer.35.17\" class=\"v24_35_17\">17</sup>Therefore, thus says the <span class=\"nd\">Lord</span>, the God of hosts, the God of Israel: Behold, I am bringing upon Judah and all the inhabitants of Jerusalem all the disaster that I have pronounced against them, because I have spoken to them and they have not listened, I have called to them and they have not answered.\u201d</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"v24_35_18\"><sup id=\"Jer.35.18\" class=\"v24_35_18\">18</sup>But to the house of the Rechabites Jeremiah said, \u201cThus says the <span class=\"nd\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: Because you have obeyed the command of Jonadab your father and kept all his precepts and done all that he commanded you, </span><span class=\"v24_35_19\"><sup id=\"Jer.35.19\" class=\"v24_35_19\">19</sup>therefore thus says the <span class=\"nd\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: Jonadab the son of Rechab shall never lack a man to stand before me.\u201d</span></p>\n</div>\n", 
