of Hazor!</span></p>\n<p class=\"qr\"><span class=\"v24_49_30\">declares the <span class=\"nd\">Lord</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v24_49_30\">For Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v24_49_30\">has made a plan against you</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v24_49_30\">and formed a purpose against you.</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v24_49_31\"><sup id=\"Jer.49.31\" class=\"v24_49_31\">31</sup>\u201cRise up, advance against a nation at ease,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v24_49_31\">that dwells securely,</span></p>\n<p class=\"qr\"><span class=\"v24_49_31\">declares the <span class=\"nd\">Lord</span>,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v24_49_31\">that has no gates or bars,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v24_49_31\">that dwells alone.</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v24_49_32\"><sup id=\"Jer.49.32\" class=\"v24_49_32\">32</sup>Their camels shall become plunder,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v24_49_32\">their herds of livestock a spoil.</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v24_49_32\">I will scatter to every wind</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v24_49_32\">those who cut the corners of their hair,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v24_49_32\">and I will bring their calamity</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v24_49_32\">from every side of them,</span></p>\n<p class=\"qr\"><span class=\"v24_49_32\">declares the <span class=\"nd\">Lord</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v24_49_33\"><sup id=\"Jer.49.33\" class=\"v24_49_33\">33</sup>Hazor shall become a haunt of jackals,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v24_49_33\">an everlasting waste;</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v24_49_33\">no man shall dwell there;</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v24_49_33\">no man shall sojourn in her.\u201d</span></p>\n<h3 class=\"s1\">Judgment on Elam</h3>\n<p class=\"p\"><span